{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2283720/extras/bnBN3.gif?t=1732920800\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to City of Despair: Shadows Over Tokyo, an immersive RPG experience where you'll gather and enhance your equipment to face off against relentless alien foes. Capture and fuse monsters to forge new, formidable allies, strategically align your attack patterns for maximum devastation, and unleash unrivaled damage in thrilling battles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">STORY</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In the heart of Tokyo, an apocalyptic nightmare unfolds as an unforgiving earthquake, triggered by a meteorite impact, shatters the city. But that's not all \u2013 alien monstrosities emerge, leaving devastation in their wake. Amidst the chaos, college student Tristan survives and, alongside 2 fearless girls from Force X, embarks on a perilous journey to reunite with his beloved Takaoka. Can Tristan find his way back to her in the midst of Tokyo's apocalypse? Discover the fate of Tokyo as it grapples with this otherworldly menace.</p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Begin the Journey","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2283720/1b5590f41a95d2c8f6c1ffba5655084823b6f9cc.jpg"},{"name":"Where Are You My Love","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2283720/d71267f238b3ead25c230eb5b5f740a37f14a93f.jpg"},{"name":"Someone To Risk My Life","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2283720/0712b7ab053a31b7ea7424b6b7650416fec661db.jpg"},{"name":"A Path To Walk Alone","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2283720/fc97b25962b2a77c36125ce6a4ca918100d87b77.jpg"},{"name":"March Toward That Meteorite","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2283720/c8ce634